        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Willing to do the Jews a pleasure; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " as his predecessor, Felix, before him, ",
        "children": []
